_sText:
After installing:

unzip files into your map file in the cstrike folder


TO ADD TO SERVER:

1.unzip files and put in an easy spot, desktop is a good spot.

2.upload maps into the map folder of your server.

3.download the maplist and mapcycle text files onto desktop

4.add the EXACT file name into both text files.

5.upload the new maplist and mapcycle files to server.

6.restart server

7.ENJOY!
